The dataset used in this project was sourced from Roboflow:

YOLOv7 Trash Dataset: https://universe.roboflow.com/yolov7-trash-detection-group/yolov7-trash-dataset-v5-05-04-2023

Due to file size limitations, the dataset is not included in this repository. Instead, it is stored externally on Google Drive:

Dataset Access: https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1oCQbCwR5qiHbGyEurkicpqj5FfZpLWQr

The dataset is provided in YOLO format and was preprocessed using a custom conversion script (yolo_to_classifier.py) to generate a binary classification dataset (trash / no_trash) for model training.
